 Nasty business that was.
 Almost got meself killed.
 Young, stupid and rash.
 Also, quite a lucky bastard.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
James expression seemed to change somewhat.
 He removed his hands from the table and for a moment sat still, looking
 at Ethan intensely.
 He then ordered another drink from Loui, who seemed to keep a watchful
 eye at their table more so than the others and nodded promptly, disappearing
 at the back for a couple of minutes.
 When James spoke next, he was lighting up Ethan's last cigarette, Ethan
 affording nothing but a stunned surprise and a deep furrow:
\end_layout

