 James was toying with the ice in his glass when a slight grin formed on
 his face, droplets of sweat running down his forehead, glistening dimly
 in the hazy, poor lighting of the Metropolitaine:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

A better chance than cricket, true enough.
