\begin_layout Standard
James shrugged, his large set of shoulders tensing up his fatigues almost
 to the point of tearing.
 He then told Ethan:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

He could be already dead, you know that.
 He might be a white English doctor, but no matter how useful he may prove
 to any captor, bullets are not very picky.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ethan went on, his fists clenching instinctively, his eyes shining with
