\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Then I'll bring back the body to Glasgow and lay him down in the ground.
 I'll do what I can, James.
 I'll do anything.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
James fixed his stare on Ethan, as if he was measuring him up:
