\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Is that some sick joke, Mr.
 Owls? People died tonight, for God's sake!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

It could have been worse.
 There could have been more dead on that trail tonight.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A flash of lightning cast a freakish shadow in the small guestroom.
 A few moments passed before the sound of thunder rolled by, when Ludwig
 managed to speak again:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

What kind of person says such a thing? These people..
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
