\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Our camp was attacked.
 Tribal lords.
 Little more than feral men, they came one day and wanted to loot everything.
 Including the women.
 Some of us tried to put up a fight.
 Perhaps it was a mistake.
 During the shooting, a few had the chance to run away.
 Andy with some of the guides stayed behind, buy us time.
 He was bleeding when..
 He..
 He gave me this cross.
 He was a believer, you see.
 Funny, no?
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


