 I knew when I saw you that you're a good man.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

You don't want to know the half of it, doctor,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

