 It'd be a fantastic piece, a world first,
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 Ethan said and aimed the camera at Yuembe.
 He took on a haughty pose like a model, indeed the kind of self-gratifying
 stance photographers tend to think is fit for nobility portraits.
 The camera clicked, and Ethan rolled the film a couple more times, taking
 a few more shots.
 Then Yuembe yanked the camera off its straps suddenly, and Ethan felt his
 plan wasn't working the way it should.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

I'll keep that film.
 I like pictures; but I don't like the publicity.
