 Pretty soon, one of them shouted back from the impromptu hospital.
 Another was holding a vest with a red cross painted on it.
 Some groggy voices and malformed protests were put down after a few slaps
 and kicks laid the patients back on their beds for good.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Yuembe shouted back more orders, looking pissed; veins shot from his temples
