 His mortal wound was remarkably clean; the bullet had went straight through
 the heart, imploding it and settling down the exit velocity to a lot less
 damaging value.
 The other one just dashed towards a low-walled flower fence and jumped
 over, creeping away back into a semblance of adequate cover.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ethan went past the church's entrance and saw the sisters hugging around
