\end_inset

Nicole! Check the church!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As he did so, Nicole had already reappeared, this time with a Beretta in
 hand; she moved along hugging the walls with all the care in the world.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Ethan could see the sunlight etching shadows inside the church, but not
 a shadow that moved.
 As he came closer he yelled:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
