 Ethan gave a mock salute and thanked him, while Nicole started the engine
 and drove off slowly towards the bridge.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
After a few yards Ethan looked back through the mirror, and saw the lieutenant
 still shaking his head; he noticed a smile and then a few laughs from the
 guards.
 He was joking; that was good.
 That meant they thought they were probably crazy; which wasn't that far
 off from reality.
 Nicole asked him then:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
