 been out, the LZ could be days away.
 And even if by some stroke of luck or genius that he couldn't really bother
 to believe in at that time, even if he did somehow escape, there was no
 telling whether he'd on time.
 No, he corrected himself.
 If they'd be there in time.
 Him and Andy.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Because if he was being held captive in this place, there was a good chance
 Andy would be around as well.
 Unless they had a whole network of caches, outposts and storage facilities
 made out of concrete, he could very well be in the next room.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Outside, he heard someone approaching once more.
