\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 came the reply, filled with finality.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
James nodded silently and hang up slowly.
 He turned around then and peeked through the window blinds; he saw the
 garden plaza, and the same, tiny swarm of men that he saw everyday.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\shape italic
